DefaultReaderConfiguration.fullDescription: Collects web-related events and device information from McAfee Web Gateway v6.x and higher appliances.

file.toolTipText: Directory or path to read from

string.toolTipText: Hostname of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

integer.toolTipText: Port number of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

select.toolTipText: Data routing (normalized alerts to Manager and/or raw data to nDepth)

integer.toolTipText: Number of seconds between log reads

FastField.defaultValue: Status Code: $7, Media Type: "$8", Extension: "$9", Media Type Status: "$10"

FastPattern.description: 6, FileAuditFailure: errors, Mobile Code Filter failed
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Mobile Code Filter: failed to (?:open|load)

FastPattern.description: 15, PolicyModify: audit, new action Block and system logNew created
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*\baudit\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] \[[A-Z]+\] .+ [-/+\w]+ [\d.]+ "new action Block and system logNew created from Block and system log" "[^"]*" [-\[\]\w.]* "[-\w. ]*" "[^"]*"

FastPattern.description: 20, SoftwareUpdate: update, Extension list, new version
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bupdate\.log [A-Z]+:\[[-/+\w: ]+\] \d+ - (?:Extension list download successful|new version: [-\w.]+, files to download: \d+)
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Old configuration found and migrated\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Secure Web Cache: +(?:Reinitializing cache database|disk storage enabled)

FastPattern.description: 26, ServiceInfo: migration, successfully copied to file

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bmigration\.log \. Added useragent of IE8 to [\w.]+\.

FastPattern.description: 28, ServiceInfo: migration, Lowered the stack size
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bmigration\.log \. Lowered the stack size for HTTP Proxy threads\.

FastPattern.description: 29, ServiceInfo: migration, Next Hop Proxies migrated
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bmigration\.log \. Next Hop Proxies migrated to new format containing "and ip" condition\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bmigration\.log \. To force update of McAfee Gateway Anti-Malware
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bmigration\.log \. Value of setting [\w.]+ set to \d+\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bmigration\.log \. Wrote version number in file
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bwcf\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] \d+ equal, \d+ modified, \d+ copy, \d+ register, \d+ directories\.

FastPattern.description: 43, ServiceInfo: wcf, cksum command line length

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bmigration\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] : Migration from version [\d.]+, build \d+ started\.
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] cannot connect to AV update server \([-\w.]+ [\w, ]+\), return code: \d+

FastField.defaultValue: cannot connect to AV update server

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Cannot load certificate '.+', key = [a-f\d]+, id = \d+, addHost = '[\d.]+'

FastPattern.description: 52, ServiceWarning: errors, Can not load CRL
55, ServiceWarning: errors, Failed to load engine
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Failed to load and initialize [-\w. ]+ engine, error code \d+

FastFormatter.condition: Failed to load and initialize ([-\w. ]+) engine,.*

FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?(\w+)\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] McAfee Gateway Anti-Malware Engine failed to scan '(.+)' - (error code .+)
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] McAfee Gateway Anti-Malware Engine failed to scan '.+' - error code

FastField.defaultValue: McAfee Gateway Anti-Malware Engine failed to scan "$4"

FastFormatter.condition: Failed to load and initialize ([-\w. ]+) engine,.*

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Information: No settings container for file [-/\w.]+ available!

FastFormatter.condition: No settings container for file ([-/\w.]+) available
FastFormatter.format: No settings container for file "$6" available

FastPattern.description: 59, ServiceWarning: errors, The license is expired

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bwcf\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] no checksum file found in "[-/\w.]+"

FastPattern.description: 62, UserAuthAudit: audit, visited the support page
63, UserDisable: errors, Denying access failed retries
FastPattern.matcher: (\d+) ([-\w.]+) MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?(\w+)\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Denying access to user '([^']+)', connected from ([-\w.]*) \(([\d.]+)\), after (\d+) failed retries.*
FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] Denying access to user '[^']+', connected from [-\w.]* \([\d.]+\), after \d+ failed retries
\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\bMPClusterControl\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\]: Sending '[^']+' notification to ICAP Server \[\d+\]

FastFormatter.condition: Sending '([^']+)' notification to ICAP Server \[(\d+)\] for policy: '([^"]+)'.*
FastFormatter.format: Sending "$6" notification to ICAP Server [$7] for policy "$8"

FastFormatter.condition: Sending '([^']+)' notification to ICAP Server \[(\d+)\] with shmem name='([^']+)' & size='(\d+)'
FastFormatter.format: Sending "$6" notification to ICAP Server [$7] with shmem name="$8" & size=$9

FastPattern.pattern: \d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?\berrors\.log \[[-/+\w: ]+\] LDAP [Ss]erver [\d.]+: (?:handled error -?\d+ '.+'|unhandled error -?\d+) in line \d+

^\d+ [-\w.]+ MSWG\[\d+\]: .*?access\.log #block_res src_ip server_ip "auth_user" policy "attribute" time_stamp "req_line" status_code bytes_to_client "referer" "user_agent" "attribute" "media_type" "profile" elapsed_time "virus_name" "rep_level"
